Welcome to the new Drow Areas of Richterm's Retreat!

The mysterious Underdark of Nordock is full of surprises and adventures. Please enjoy the latest addition to Richterm's Retreat, and hopefully the Drow subrace will have more to do...away from the surface. There is only one way to the Underdark from the surface, and that is via Loknar.

If you have any suggestions or feedback, please leave it at the Richterm's Retreat Forums at http://www.nordock.net. There is a Drow forum there called The Underdark. The password for entrance into that forum is spiderqueen.

Have fun!

-Jarketh Thavin, Drow DM and Underdark Engineer.
